TextEng: How do you know my name?
How you know me name?
I think I'll be going now.
Sorry, you must have me confused with someone else.
Text: 미안하지만, 나를 다른 사람으로 착각한 것 같아.

TextEng: Me go now.
Me think you not know me. You thinking of some other one.
Text: 나 너 나 몰라. 너 다른 사람 생각하는 거야.

TextEng: Why are you so interested in Lady Aribeth?
Text: 왜 아리베스 경에게 그렇게 관심이 많아?

TextEng: How's your training going, Silk?
Can I ask you some questions?
Why you want spy on Aribeth?
How you training going, Silk?
Me want ask you some questions.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard those rumors about a cure for the plague?
How do you like training here at the Academy?
What you know 'bout plague?
You hear stuff 'bout cure for plague?
You like training at Academy?
I thought you were just a spy!
Me thought you just be spy!
Text: 나 너 그냥 첩자인 줄 알았어!

TextEng: Sounds like you're a little jealous.
It sound like you maybe jealous.
Don't worry - I still want to get together.
Text: 걱정 마 - 나 아직도 만나고 싶어.

TextEng: You no worry - me still want see you later.
Text: 너 걱정 마 - 나 아직도 나중에 보고 싶어.

TextEng: Actually, I can't get together with you later after all.
Text: 사실, 나중에 같이 있을 수 없을 것 같아.

TextEng: Me sorry. Me no can see you later.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 나중에 못 봐.

TextEng: Forget it, Silk. I'm not interested in someone who's been stalking me.
Text: 됐어, 실크. 날 스토킹한 사람한테는 관심 없어.

TextEng: I find dangerous women *very* interesting.
You're really not my type, Silk.
Me like danger type girls.
Me not be interested in that kind of woman!
Me no want date girl who be stalking me.
Text: 나 스토킹하는 여자랑 데이트 안 해.

TextEng: That's kind of a personal question.
That not be none of you business!
I'd like that, Silk.
Sorry, but I'm not interested.
Uh... I'm already going with somebody. Sorry, Silk.
Text: 어... 나 이미 누군가랑 가기로 했어. 미안해, 실크.

TextEng: Me like that, Silk.
Me not interested. Sorry.
Uh... me got date already. Sorry, Silk.
Text: 어... 나 이미 약속 있어. 미안해, 실크.

TextEng: Back off, you psychotic freak!
Me not like you! You be psycho freak girl!
Can I ask you some questions?
Me want ask you some questions.
What are you talking about?
What you mean by that?
Goodbye.
Where can I find Shade?
Where Shade be?
